35:09.625 --> 35:10.541
Ursula?

35:11.041 --> 35:12.541
No. No, I...

35:15.083 --> 35:16.291
I have another one.

35:18.625 --> 35:19.541
Eva.

35:21.416 --> 35:22.708
Eva's the little one.

35:23.708 --> 35:24.625
Oh.

35:25.666 --> 35:26.666
You know, um...

35:29.833 --> 35:32.708
you cannot just fall to pieces right now,

35:32.708 --> 35:34.833
because you...

35:37.041 --> 35:38.625
you were amazing today.

35:39.833 --> 35:42.666
That was such a difficult mission,

35:42.666 --> 35:46.583
and you were so determined
to save Lisa's husband.

35:46.583 --> 35:47.875
And, well,

35:48.750 --> 35:49.750
we did it.

35:55.833 --> 35:57.416
But you have to

35:58.958 --> 36:00.708
keep moving forward

36:01.958 --> 36:03.500
because...

36:38.916 --> 36:39.791
Lisa.

37:11.750 --> 37:14.500
Just thinking of you
kept me alive in there.

37:52.833 --> 37:54.375
I'm a criminal too.

37:58.166 --> 37:59.041
I know.

38:03.666 --> 38:05.958
Why does Madame Nouget own this house?

38:16.125 --> 38:18.416
She worked for me for years in Paris.

38:19.958 --> 38:21.625
Knew what I was doing there.

38:22.333 --> 38:24.083
She knows what we're doing here?

38:34.583 --> 38:36.625
I was smuggling Jews to Palestine.

38:38.333 --> 38:40.333
And when the Nazis came to Paris...

38:42.750 --> 38:44.041
she helped me escape.

38:47.291 --> 38:48.583
I owe her everything.

38:54.166 --> 38:55.958
One day, I'll have to leave here too.

38:57.208 --> 38:59.375
But then I'll leave her with this house.

39:07.416 --> 39:10.041
This is a new world, Varian.

39:12.333 --> 39:13.958
The old rules don't apply.

39:20.541 --> 39:22.416
But if the rules don't apply,

39:23.833 --> 39:25.833
