39:29.625 --> 39:30.625
In ourselves.

39:33.625 --> 39:34.625
In each other.

40:36.833 --> 40:37.666
Uh...

40:37.666 --> 40:38.750
Good morning.

40:46.875 --> 40:48.958
I had the best night.

40:58.875 --> 41:00.791
