41:01.541 --> 41:04.208
It is not our language that has gone mad.

41:06.166 --> 41:07.125
No.

41:10.208 --> 41:12.791
One day
Germany will recover from all this.

41:13.833 --> 41:15.208
One day, maybe.

41:16.458 --> 41:17.833
But we live now.

41:22.625 --> 41:24.583
Right now I feel very much alive.

42:24.708 --> 42:25.958
<i>My dear brother.</i>

42:27.041 --> 42:30.708
<i>I have finally managed to get
American visas for both of us.</i>

42:32.041 --> 42:35.708
