at the American consulate in Marseille.</i>

42:36.416 --> 42:40.291
<i>I know you don't like
people telling you what to do,</i>

42:41.208 --> 42:44.833
<i>but</i>, <i>out of respect for our parents,
please collect the visa.</i>

42:45.625 --> 42:49.458
<i>Come meet me in Lisbon
so we can travel to America together.</i>

42:51.458 --> 42:53.416
<i>We've both already lost so much.</i>

42:55.041 --> 42:57.000
<i>I refuse to leave you behind.</i>

42:58.208 --> 43:00.333
<i>Your loving sister, Ursula.</i>

43:24.125 --> 43:25.000
Bingham.

43:27.958 --> 43:31.708
Thanks for meeting me here.
- I'm sorry about Reese. I had no idea.

43:33.333 --> 43:36.458
It was humiliating, but he's harmless.
I'm working around him.

43:36.458 --> 43:38.333
Didn't Patterson
try to kick you out of France?

43:38.333 --> 43:40.083
I don't give up that easily.

43:40.083 --> 43:43.375
Good.
<i>-</i> Yeah, I need you to do something for me.

43:44.750 --> 43:48.791
Her name is Hannah Arendt. I've got
