44:47.333 --> 44:48.208
tops.

44:50.041 --> 44:50.958
Thank you.

45:19.750 --> 45:20.708
Paul.

45:23.625 --> 45:25.250
Thank you for freeing our men.

45:25.250 --> 45:26.166
Our men?

